title: Grazing Daysi
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Delivery, Take-out, Fusion, Ayurvedic
description: Family-friendly place serving home-style food prepared with Ayurvedic principles, opened summer 2013. Offers an open menu: choose a dish made from what's available and what you feel like. Uses natural ingredients and organic where possible; no white flour, white sugar, or processed food. Gluten-free options.
